Messer Attribute Modifier Plug-in
=================================

The Messer Attribute Modifier Plug-in (AMP) messes up any piece of geometry by
randomising the vertex positions by a factor provided by the user.

Environment Variables
---------------------

KATANA_HOME  The Katana installation directory at compile-time

Building
--------

1. Ensure the environment variables listed above have been set.
2. Run 'make'.
3. Copy 'out/Messer.so' to the 'Libs' subdirectory within a Katana
   resources path.
